@start
on-arrival: {!
Q.started = 1;
// time elapsed (in months)
Q.time = 1;
Q.year = 4000;
Q.month = 1;
// how many actions have been taken this month?
Q.month_actions = 0;

// 0 = normal difficulty, 1 = hard mode, 2 = hard mode no saves
Q.difficulty = 0;
Q.historical_mode = 0;

// party resources
Q.resources = 100;
// party dues
Q.dues = 2;

// the state of the party
// overall dissent reduces every increase in party support.
Q.dissent = 0.05;
Q.dissent_percent = 5;

// factions
Q.factions = ['pragmatists', 'populists', 'cronyists'];
// should this be normalized to 100%?
Q.pragmatists_strength = 15;
Q.pragmatists_dissent = 20;
Q.populists_strength = 30;
Q.populists_dissent = 0;
Q.cronyists_strength = 25;
Q.cronyists_dissent = 5;

// inter-party relations
Q.mcp_relation = 20;
Q.dissident_relations = 0;
// note: model the multitude of dissident groups

// Advisors/Leaders
Q.n_advisors = 3;
// timer - this decrements by 1 every turn, and is set to 5 whenever an advisor action is used, so that you can only use one advisor action every 5 months.
// let's just put all of the timers here...
// most party affairs and government affairs cards are on a timer.
Q.timers = ['fundraising', 'media', 'rally'];
Q.advisor_action_timer = 0;
Q.advisor_loss_timer = 0;

Q.fun_value = Math.floor(Math.random() * 100) + 1;

!}
set-bg: img/map_2.jpg
new-page: true

> *"Meline is one of the few planets in the galaxy which can support human life without a need for terraforming. This should have allowed it to blossom freely without needing to depend upon corporations - alas, it was not to be! The anti-monopoly laws set out by the pioneers seem ever so fickle in their absence, and the once hopeful unification of the planet seems now but a front for consolidation. Only an equally consolidated effort of all Melinians behind a socialist party can defend it from reduction to factory-world."*

 - Ronald T., *For a Meline Socialist Party*, 3964

Welcome to Meline, a planet beset by corporate exploitation, oppression and hegemony, as with most planets. Meline is unique in being utterly unimportant in the grand scheme of things, and yet still finds itself of acute interest to several megacorporations for its rarity. What will you do?

- @1928_main: Begin (normal difficulty)
